metadata.name: Guppy
metadata.description: Guppies are resilient that they survive in some of the harshest waterways known to many. These 22,222 Guppies will be swimming in the Ether that will act as VIP passes in the Pokuna. Guppies are a way to show your loyalty to the positive causes that will be carried out in the Pokuna. Get involved and you will be rewarded. Visit www.pokuna.io
